{"tid":647510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好放錯重點，所有問題源自每日150單程證！","createTime":"2018-04-30T01:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T16:43:26.000Z","uid":168703,"like":152,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"faf1a049b33fb1f107b4da0524be7228ec5e9448","tid":647510,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T01:44:24.000Z","msg":"許智峰乜乜乜話之佢啦，真唔真普選都係其次！<br />\n<br />\n點解每日地鐵蝗多過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解新屋邨全部講蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解起極樓都唔夠屋住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解民香港人上唔到樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解公立醫院唔夠人手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解交稅俾綜緩養懶人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解派糖益哂蝗你無份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解民建聯咁多人支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所有問題，源自支那新移民，唔係班蝗不停落黎霸哂啲居住空間，地產霸權都唔會好似今日今日咁無法無天。<br />\n<br />\n新移民威脅我地各方面，包括最基本嘅衣、食、住、行、醫療、福利、治安，所以當務之急係唔好俾其他嘢distract到，集中向停止每日150單程證目標進發，喺所有渠道宣傳！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n乜撚嘢平反六四呀嗰啲唔撚使再講(關我撚事？)，集中火力，每日都要講停止每日150單程證！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a800c663707c53e2259376a0c30f7fa3d7ec173f","tid":647510,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T01:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f2351b258ccbf3ba866c21bb46a6dcd29da5b04","tid":647510,"uid":168703,"like"